                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "高天之歌"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素伤害</span>，召唤<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">暴风之眼</span>。</p><p></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/4e6c64424bb066f0f74936bf7fbc1b5a_8287937605147207100.png",
                "id": "talent92847",
                "key": "风神之诗",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "风神之诗"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召唤物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结束阶段：</span>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素伤害</span>，对方切换到<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">距离我方出战角色最近的角色</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：2</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方角色或召唤物引发扩散反应后：</span>转换此牌的元素类型，改为造成被扩散的元素类型的伤害。（离场前仅限一次）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_1350279389680826803.png",
                "id": "talent56773",
                "key": "暴风之眼",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/481ff844d1ba46461024c9ade7a0e5db_7305731629271551358.png",
                "title": "暴风之眼"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>和已附着的元素发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">扩散（冰）</span>：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点冰元素伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">扩散（水）</span>：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点水元素伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">扩散（火）</span>：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点火元素伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">扩散（雷）</span>：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点雷元素伤害</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/27/88072335/c97292d96456bfe4abeca16bfce801e4_6853646017909304028.png",
                "id": "talent96188",
                "key": "风元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "风元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">风域</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出战状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方执行「切换角色」行动时：</span>少花费1个元素骰。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：2</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/27/88072335/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_3677771837683644178.png",
